column4:
See why so many travelers make Nasa Hotel BMC their small hotel of choice when visiting Sisophon. Providing an ideal mix of value, comfort and convenience, it offers an array of amenities designed for travelers like you.
Free wifi is offered to guests, and rooms at Nasa Hotel BMC offer air conditioning, a refrigerator, and a minibar.
During your stay, take advantage of some of the amenities offered, including a concierge. For travelers arriving by car, free parking is available.
During your visit, be sure to check out a popular Sisophon Asian restaurants such as Kim Heng, which is a short distance from Nasa Hotel BMC.
We’re sure you’ll enjoy your stay at Nasa Hotel BMC as you experience all of the things Sisophon has to offer.
